清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"b656968d7a053f27f556b653904f9857","url_token":"13813246726","name":"浩然梦想家","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-47f3df352a6ad421946b082e784bc273_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-47f3df352a6ad421946b082e784bc273_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/b656968d7a053f27f556b653904f9857","user_type":"people","headline":"改变世界的梦想，留给下辈子吧。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560511727","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545845272,"updated_time":1545845272,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":18,"content":"\u003cp\u003e白天看到这个问题只是笑了笑，小孩子嘛，心高气傲，年少轻狂没什么。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是逐渐升温之后，部分回答我真的是不太看的下去。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我的出发点不是说这个高中生有证明的可能性，在我看来，这就像一个人问：我100米只需5秒就可以跑完，请问我可以代表中国国家队参加奥运会吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是恳请各位键盘侠嘴下留情，你可以直言规劝，甚至是冷嘲热讽，让一个孩子走上正路。但永远不应该是人身攻击，网络暴力，甚至是针对家人的咒骂。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e年少轻狂是无知，网络暴力是无德。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561926830,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"8980d37769465f49ad5f2bfb1fcac69e","url_token":"ban-zhi-jun","name":"半知菌","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4856daff56c951e902cbda0346f2f732_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4856daff56c951e902cbda0346f2f732_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/8980d37769465f49ad5f2bfb1fcac69e","user_type":"people","headline":"文昌鱼","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561926830","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546015644,"updated_time":1546015644,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"如果我能打破跳远的世界纪录，我会有资格被选进省队吗？如果我长得和吴彦祖小李子一样帅，校花会不会对我另眼相看？事实上，证明哥德巴赫猜想这个事件的意义和难度要远远大于保送什么的行为，所以我认为这是一个荒唐的命题。其实问题者认为保送本身就是一个终极理想的人生目标，从而寻求一种超自然的外力达到对目标征服的意淫。\u003cbr\u003e可是，你知道真正的天才是怎么样的吗？当伽罗华在孤独而凄冷的深夜，面对着即刻的死亡，在纸上潦草而绝望地挥洒自己无与伦比的数学天赋的时候，他可能宁愿自己不是那个天才。当梵高的眼前只有混乱而绝美的星夜，颤抖的笔触无法触及爱人的心灵，旷世的才华却被巴黎美院的专家踩在脚底，他可能宁愿自己不是那个天才。伟大的天才要忍受伟大的不幸。他们想得到世人的认可，谋求一个被社会公允的“位置”时，他的天赋的发泄却早已远远超过那个无聊的位置，到了高的光明之处，就像高飞的伊卡洛斯，他们从不在乎明亮的阳光会烧灼自己闪亮的羽毛。","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561742510,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"484833e8ae5437b0f455b4189ef8378f","url_token":"zhang-hua-yu-88-96","name":"张华宇","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/484833e8ae5437b0f455b4189ef8378f","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561742510","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545995246,"updated_time":1545995350,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"\u003cp\u003e话说，这问题能否改成:如果证明了哥猜，可不可以被任命为牛津卢卡斯数学教授？？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这样至少对哥德巴赫同志尊重一点\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":564011612,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408