ww.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561464936","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545969698,"updated_time":1545969698,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":17,"content":"\u003cp\u003e你，山口山千年来不世出的大领主，横扫了宇宙中的极恶势力燃烧军团，一举击败最强邪神萨格拉斯。歼星舰、圣光炮、魔能机甲，什么样的神级科技没见过？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e结果回到地球，转身又拿出了原始的投石车、弓箭，试图争霸世界……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e——————————————————————————————————————\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e中学时，有一阵我喜欢在上课时写小说，对自己的文采颇为自得，认为自己写的文章“完美无瑕，无懈可击，掷之地亦有金石声”，将来成为下一个韩寒问题不大。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那时写的小说，现在已经不知道扔到哪里去了……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e有远大理想是好事，但理想不是买彩票撞大运，从来都是一步一个脚印走出来的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果你的理想不是证明哥德巴赫猜想，而是保送清华北大，那你很可能并不具备实力摘取这颗“数学皇冠上的明珠”。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560221075,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"cfcc6614f92c2a0e85ddca50bdc9b134","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560221075","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545819649,"updated_time":1545819649,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":9,"content":"\u003cp\u003e如果真能的话。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e清华北大即将开始跳过各种严格要求开始特聘您为教授乃至数学院院长，并建立以您的名字命名的数学专属班（参考清华姚班）。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e直接升为两院院士，哪怕工程院与您无关，也会扛着各种审批死乞白赖的请求您加入工程院。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e国外各个大学即将向您抛来橄榄枝，终身教授，正式教授，挂名教授，国籍身份。薪酬待遇等统统不是问题。但我国会就此展开严肃抗议并通过各种手段强势挽留，包括但不限于送钱送房\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e提前锁定今年各大数学奖项。已经确定但未颁发的直接改成您的名字再发布，否则直接命名为野鸡奖项即可。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559467935,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559467935","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e207385b806d8cb998df0e3ded6e0f10_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545729502,"updated_time":1545730225,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":19,"content":"\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e919ed8b142a826e3c094876a38b7f7b_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"290\" data-rawheight=\"302\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e919ed8b142a826e3c094876a38b7f7b_b.jpg\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"290\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='290'%20height='302'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"290\" data-rawheight=\"302\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e919ed8b142a826e3c094876a38b7f7b_b.jpg\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"290\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e919ed8b142a826e3c094876a38b7f7b_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\